16:16.851 --> 16:17.935
Well, hey...

16:19.103 --> 16:20.688
there is an upside.

16:20.772 --> 16:22.064
Which is?

16:22.148 --> 16:24.400
- You didn't burn the house down.

16:30.948 --> 16:32.408
