18:49.837 --> 18:51.756
Is this the first time
they meet in the play?

18:51.839 --> 18:53.090
Yeah.
What do you think?

18:54.258 --> 18:55.301
It's good, but...

18:56.427 --> 18:58.470
Never mind.

18:58.554 --> 19:00.222
-It's stupid.
-No, tell me.

19:01.557 --> 19:05.477
Well, maybe Hope should be
a voice at first.

19:05.561 --> 19:10.149
Or else people won't get that she's...
more than a person. You know?

19:10.858 --> 19:14.111
Yeah. That's... that's perfect.

19:14.195 --> 19:15.404
- Really?
- Yeah.

19:15.487 --> 19:17.073
That's actually what it needs.

19:18.449 --> 19:21.077
Thanks for ditching girls' night to help.

19:21.160 --> 19:22.369
Well, I'm pretty sure I got ditched.

19:22.453 --> 19:24.872
But... you're welcome.

19:25.915 --> 19:27.416
Hey, do you want to play Hope?

19:28.334 --> 19:30.753
I've been having
a really hard time casting the part...

19:32.088 --> 19:34.090
but I think you'd be perfect for it.

19:34.716 --> 19:37.093
You're really awesome, Lola.

19:39.553 --> 19:41.097
