19:42.639 --> 19:43.891
Why is that?

19:45.351 --> 19:46.769
Because I like you.

19:48.229 --> 19:49.981
And I tried not to, but I do.

19:51.523 --> 19:54.360
And I'm worried if we spend
too much time together...

19:55.652 --> 19:57.822
we might do something
that will get us both in trouble.

19:58.530 --> 19:59.699
Like what?

20:04.787 --> 20:06.497
Are you sure you want this?

20:32.732 --> 20:34.566
Are you thinking about Tristan?

20:37.737 --> 20:39.530
Was that a weird thing to say?

20:40.489 --> 20:41.657
Very.

20:42.408 --> 20:44.326
-Thought you might be feeling--
-Guilty?

20:45.244 --> 20:46.287
Yeah.

20:47.872 --> 20:49.415
So...

20:49.498 --> 20:50.499
do you?

20:52.543 --> 20:53.585
Yeah.

21:02.762 --> 21:04.346
But I also feel good.

21:07.183 --> 21:09.476
