22:11.663 --> 22:13.707
But you drank.

22:13.790 --> 22:15.292
Was it someone else?

22:15.376 --> 22:16.793
No...

22:16.878 --> 22:18.963
I guess I thought that
if you thought that we did it,

22:19.046 --> 22:23.300
then I could feel like
my relationship with him was important.

22:25.136 --> 22:26.637
--Don't laugh.

22:26.720 --> 22:27.846
No, it's just...

22:27.930 --> 22:30.266
