about living up to you.

22:31.017 --> 22:33.895
But if you didn't, that's great.
That means none of us are doing it.

22:33.978 --> 22:35.897
Only you would find that exciting, Shay.

22:35.980 --> 22:38.024
You know what,
it is probably for the best anyway.

22:38.107 --> 22:40.067
Sex just complicates things.

22:40.151 --> 22:41.277
Only if you let it.

22:46.782 --> 22:48.575
